# Agent memory files
# CLAUDE.md is a shared project guide and is tracked with the root live docs.
AGENTS.md

# docs/ work notes are local-only by default (plans/specs/reviews/completion
# reports). Already-tracked files are unaffected. Only explicitly curated
# governance docs, executable implementation specs, and docs/protocol/ should be
# re-included below so review-relevant handoff material is not hidden.
/docs/*
!/docs/protocol/
!/docs/engineering-constitution.md
!/docs/2026-07-03-web-renderer-shared-package-implementation-plan.md
!/docs/2026-07-03-web-renderer-shared-package-implementation-plan-review.md
# Per-round completion + audit reports: tracked so the evidence chain is in git
# (independent audit, completion report, pre-delete audit points, doc-gap audits).
!/docs/*完成情况*.md
!/docs/*审计*.md
!/docs/*audit*.md

# Local-only handoff/exec-plan clutter (untracked; files kept on disk).
# Precise paths — do NOT ignore the whole handoffs/ or .exec-plan/ trees,
# since both contain tracked files (older handoffs, committed plan states).
handoffs/handoff-20260702-1511.md
handoffs/handoff-20260702-1839.md
handoffs/handoff-20260702-2053.md
handoffs/handoff-20260703-0132.md
